info.name: Teste Software
info.description:
These tests must be executed in this order, because they have dependencies.

The order:

1. Login
2. Create a new entry
3. Search entry by description
    1. save the ID of the entry created on the step 2
4. List entries from first page
5. Prepare to create a new entry
6. Prepare to edit
7. Remove a specific entry

item.name: GET - List entries from first page
GET - Prepare to create a new entry
